title: tread93
author: tread93
content: Hey Guys, I am looking for a polymerbit 2022 BTC Miami note, please message me if you have one for sale  I got to spend some time with Polymerbit at the conference, it was great fun trading some notes with him! He taught me so much about my own note collection, he really knows his stuff that m8. I asked him if he had any of these notes left but he only had number 1! Which of course I only drooled over a little bit  . Anyhow let me know if anything comes up, would love to work out a trade as well!Thanks, Tread93
